title: Opera on Wheels at Port Clinton City Schools (Port Clinton City School District)
text: ( Source : Port Clinton City School District ) Thanks to the Greater Port Clinton Area Arts Council (GPCAAC), Toledo Youth Opera on Wheels visited Port Clinton City Schools. The first performance was on Monday, October 26 , 2015 at Port Clinton
